headline.main: Hart, Jenkins Lead Way as No. 2 Villanova Routs Georgetown
headline.print_headline: Hart, Jenkins Lead Way as No. 2 Villanova Routs Georgetown

lead_paragraph: Cheshire cat grins flashed across the faces of Villanova senior guards Josh Hart and Kris Jenkins as they pondered coming home to the D.C. area to face Georgetown one last time.
